$17 13. Bg3 O-O-O (13... Na5 $5 $17) 14. Bxf4 $15 gxf4 15. h3 $2 (15. b4 $142
$5 $15 {and White could well hope to play on}) 15... Bxh3 $19 16. Re1 (16. b4
