Na5 $5 23. Qb5 Nxc4 24. Qxc4 fxe4 25. Rxe4 Bf5 $19) 23. Nxe4 Bxf3 $4 {
releasing the pressure on the opponent} (23... Na5 $142 24. Qb5 Nxc4 25. Qxd7+
Bxd7 (25... Kxd7 $143 26. Nf6+ (26. Nxc5+ $143 Kc6 27. Rxe8 Rxe8 $11) 26... Kc6
27. Rxe8 (27. Nxe8 $143 Nd2+ (27... Nxb2 $2 {doesn't lead to the expected
